    <title>CW needs to be buffed</title>
    <link>https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/cw-needs-to-be-buffed/71617</link>
    <description>Bring back some form of barrier that the CW can grant to someone that prevents their death or prevents others from visiting him, from any/some old iteration of this class. Keep the 3 tornados.

right now, empower is such a weak skill in general usage and pretty boring (outside of niche situations like you being in a pact with a known butler or something empowering him every night to make him immune and clear minding him etc)

on top of this, CW claims are very weak claims, probably about the same as claiming knight if nobody alive happened to visit anyone you swapped to know if you did or didnt swap

Restore CW to a claim that gives off the impact of &quot;woah this guy claims court wizard&quot; similar to someone claiming hunter or at least butler, rather than &quot;oh just a CW claim, probably evil and otherwise not very useful so let&#39;s hang him to get narrow down the list&quot;</description>
    
